T02TD2954E:33a-0: @33a * // dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2954E:33a-1: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur bar 'dod pa'i sgrub pa po dam tshig dang ldan pas gnas khang yid dang mthun par me tog sil ma bkram la sa chog la sogs pa sngon du song bas rgyu skar rnams kyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs te dbus padma 'dab brgyad la dkar po lte ba sngon po /
T02TD2954E:33a-2: mu khyud padma'i phreng bas mdzes par bskor ba /
T02TD2954E:33a-3: khyams dar dmar po la shar nas brtsams nas sna tshogs yid du 'ong ba'i khang bu bdun bdun gyis bskor bsgo bzhi mu khyud sna tshogs skar ma'i 'od 'khrug pa bri'o //
T02TD2954E:33a-4: de nas gtso bo'i mtshan ma dang /
T02TD2954E:33a-5: padma rnams la gza' brgyad kyi mtshan ma dang /
T02TD2954E:33a-6: khang bu rnams su shar nas brtsams te /
T02TD2954E:33b-18: sin dh'u ra'i sol ba dang ;
T02TD2954E:33b-25: rma bya rnams bri bar bya'o //
T02TD2954E:33b-26: de nas bum pa nyi shu rtsa dgu la rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-27: so so'i mtshan ma dri sna tshogs pas btab la /
T02TD2954E:33b-29: phyogs mtshams rnams su phur bus 'khor bar gzhag go //
T02TD2954E:33b-30: de dag gi bar bar du'ang tshon sna tshogs pa'i skud pas sbrel lo //
T02TD2954E:33b-31: bdug spos la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i yo byad ci 'byor pa bsham mo //
T02TD2954E:33b-32: de nas gza' dang rgyu skar gyi gtor ma dang /
T02TD2954E:33b-33: phyogs skyong rnams la gtor ma tshul bzhin du bsham mo //
T02TD2954E:33b-34: de nas yan lag bdun pa sngon du song bas so so'i bum par sngags dang phyag rgyas bskyed do //
T02TD2954E:33b-35: shar gyi bum pa dang po nas brtsams te smin drug dkar po zhal gcig phyag stong dang ldan pa phyag g-yas nam dung bsnams pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-36: zhal nas bdud rtsi'i rgyun 'bab pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-37: khyi dkar po la zhon pa bskyed do //
T02TD2954E:33b-38: de bzhin du gzhan 'dra ba la snar ma mdog ser ljang phyag na mda' bo che nya la zhon pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-39: mgo mdog dkar smug 'khor lo sre mo la zhon pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-40: lag mdog dkar gtun shing bsnams pa glang la zhon pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-41: nab so mdog dkar po phyag na phub ba lang la zhon pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-42: rgyal mdog dkar ser phyag na ral gri khyung la zhon pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-43: skag sngon po rnga yab bsnams pa rtal zhon pa bskyed do //
T02TD2954E:33b-44: lho phyogs su mchu mdog ser pa lag pa brgya stong grangs med pa rin po che'i rgyan rnams kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-45: phyag rnams na me bsnams pa bya la zhon ba bskyed do //
T02TD2954E:33b-46: gre mdog sngo skya phyag na chu /
T02TD2954E:33b-48: dbo mdog dmar skya phyag rnams nas /
T02TD2954E:33b-50: me bzhi mdog dkar po phyag na rlung /
T02TD2954E:33b-51: rin po che sna bzhi'i khri la gnas pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-52: nag pa mdog nag po phyag rnams na rgyal mtshan g-yag la zhon pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-53: sa ri mdog ser po phyag na sbud pa /
T02TD2954E:33b-54: gser gyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
T02TD2954E:34a-0: sa ga mdog dud ka phyag rnams @34a * //
T02TD2954E:34a-2: sbrul la zhon pa bskyed do //
T02TD2954E:34a-3: nub tu gzi brjid chen mo mdog dmar phyag rnams me long /
T02TD2954E:34a-5: snron mdog ser skya phyag rnams na bse kha sbyar /
T02TD2954E:34a-7: snrubs sku mdog dmar ser phyag rnams na dngul gyi phreng ba /
T02TD2954E:34a-9: chu stod mdog sngon mo phyag rnams na zhags pa /
T02TD2954E:34a-11: chu smad mdog ljang sngon phyag rnams na bdan bsnams pa /
T02TD2954E:34a-13: gro bzhin mdog smug po phyag rnams na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
T02TD2954E:34a-15: byi bzhin mdog dmar skya phyag rnams na sin dh'u ra'i sol ba /
T02TD2954E:34a-17: byang du mon gru mdog ljang gu phyag rnams na seng ge dkar mo /
T02TD2954E:34a-19: mon dre mdog mthing ga phyag rnams na beng mo /
T02TD2954E:34a-21: khrums stod mdog ljang ser phyag rnams la byi la khra mo bsnams pa /
T02TD2954E:34a-23: khrums smad mdog ljang sngon phyag na glang sngon po bsnams pa /
T02TD2954E:34a-25: nam gru mdog mthing ga phyag rnams na bya rgod ser po /
T02TD2954E:34a-27: tha skar mdog ljang dmar phyag na ri skegs khra mo /
T02TD2954E:34a-29: bra nye mdog dung ser rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs pas brgyan pa /
T02TD2954E:34a-30: phyag brgya stong na rma bya sngon po bsnams pa /
T02TD2954E:34a-31: zhal gcig pa zhal nas bdud rtsi'i rgyun 'bab pa rus sbal zhon pa bskyed do //
T02TD2954E:34a-32: de dag kyang sa bon kun las byung ba 'od zer brgya stong dpag tu med pa 'phro ba bskyed do //
T02TD2954E:34a-33: sngags ni aom sa sv'a h'a /
T02TD2954E:34a-61: zhes go rims kyis so so'i ye shes sems dpa' rnams bstim la /
T02TD2954E:34a-62: bum pa zhal gyi bdud rtsi chu bo'i rang bzhin du dmigs so //
T02TD2954E:34a-63: de nas mchod pa dang bstod pa'i bye brag ci rigs par byas la /
T02TD2954E:34b-0: ji ltar 'dod pa'i don la @34b gsol ba btab /
T02TD2954E:34b-1: de nas slob ma gos gsar pa gyon la /
T02TD2954E:34b-2: khrus nas bton la dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa dang /
T02TD2954E:34b-3: me tog phog pa'i las kyi lha ngo bstan pa dang /
T02TD2954E:34b-5: de nas gtor ma'i cho ga rgyas bar bya'o //
T02TD2954E:34b-6: gtor ma chu klung chen por bskyal lo //
T02TD2954E:34b-7: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing slob ma bum pa'i chus khrus bya zhing bkra shis gsol ba dang /
T02TD2954E:34b-8: tshogs ji ltar rigs par bsag go //
T02TD2954E:34b-9: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dbang bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rdo rje go cham zhes bya ba /
T02TD2954E:34b-10: dpal mar me mdzad bzang pos mdzad pa rdzogs so//
